  "👋  What is Osenpa Auto Clicker?": "👋  什么是 Osenpa Auto Clicker？",
  "Osenpa Auto Clicker is a desktop automation tool. It lets your computer click the mouse, press keyboard keys, and find colors or images on screen — all automatically, as many times as you want.\n\nThink of it like a robot that copies exactly what you tell it to do, and repeats it perfectly every time.": "Osenpa Auto Clicker 是一款桌面自动化工具。它能让您的电脑自动点击鼠标、按下键盘按键，并在屏幕上查找颜色或图像——这一切都是自动的，您可以想执行多少次就执行多少次。\n\n把它想象成一个机器人，它能准确复制您的指令，并每次都完美重复执行。",
  "📋  Steps — The Heart of Automation": "📋  步骤 — 自动化的核心",
  "Everything you want the computer to do is called a Step. You build a list of steps, and Osenpa Auto Clicker runs them in order.\n\n• KEYBOARD step — presses a key (e.g. Enter, Space, A, Ctrl+C)\n• MOUSE step — clicks at a position on screen\n• COLOR step — waits until a color appears, then clicks it\n• IMAGE step — waits until a picture appears on screen, then clicks it\n• DELAY step — pauses for a moment before continuing\n• IF COLOR / IF IMAGE — checks if something is there, and does one thing if yes, another if no\n\nTIP: Double-click any step in the list to edit it. Drag steps up and down to reorder them.": "您想让电脑做的每件事都叫做一个“步骤”。您创建一个步骤列表，Osenpa Auto Clicker 会按顺序执行它们。\n\n• 键盘步骤 — 按下一个键（如 回车、空格、A、Ctrl+C）\n• 鼠标步骤 — 在屏幕特定位置点击\n• 颜色步骤 — 等待颜色出现，然后点击它\n• 图像步骤 — 等待图像出现在屏幕上，然后点击它\n• 延迟步骤 — 暂停片刻再继续\n• 如果颜色 / 如果图像 — 检查目标是否存在，如果存在则执行一种操作，否则执行另一种操作\n\n提示：双击列表中的任何步骤进行编辑。上下拖动步骤以对它们进行重新排序。",
  "⌨️  Keyboard Panel": "⌨️  键盘面板",
  "Use the Keyboard panel to press any key or key combination.\n\n• SINGLE KEY — press one key at a time (e.g. press F5 to refresh)\n• HOTKEY COMBO — press multiple keys at once (e.g. ctrl+z to undo, ctrl+shift+s to save as)\n• REPEAT — how many times to press the key\n• INTERVAL — how long to wait between each press\n\nTIP: Click inside the KEY box and press the key you want — it gets captured automatically. No typing required.": "使用键盘面板可按下任何键或组合键。\n\n• 单键 — 一次按下一个键（例如按F5刷新）\n• 组合热键 — 一次按下多个键（例如 ctrl+z 撤消，ctrl+shift+s 另存为）\n• 重复 — 按键的次数\n• 间隔 — 每次按键之间等待的时长\n\n提示：在按键框内点击并按下所需的键——它会自动捕获。无需输入。",
  "🖱️  Mouse Panel": "🖱️  鼠标面板",
  "Use the Mouse panel to click anywhere on the screen.\n\n• FIXED COORDINATES — click at a specific X,Y position on screen\n• CURRENT CURSOR POSITION — click wherever your mouse is at the time\n• LEFT / RIGHT / MIDDLE button — choose which mouse button to click\n• DRAG — click and drag from one point to another (like drag-and-drop)\n\nTIP: Use the PICK TARGET button to click on the screen and automatically fill in the X,Y coordinates. No manual typing!": "使用鼠标面板可在屏幕上的任何位置进行点击。\n\n• 固定坐标 — 点击屏幕上特定的 X,Y 位置\n• 当前光标位置 — 在鼠标当前所在的位置点击\n• 左 / 右 / 中 键 — 选择要点击的鼠标按钮\n• 拖动 — 点击并从一点拖动到另一点（拖放）\n\n提示：使用“选择目标”按钮在屏幕上点击并自动填写 X,Y 坐标。无需手动输入！",
  "🎨  Color Detection": "🎨  颜色检测",
  "Color Detection watches the screen and clicks as soon as it spots a color you have defined.\n\n• PICK COLOR — opens a color picker to choose an exact color\n• PICK FROM SCREEN — click anywhere on your screen to grab that pixel's color\n• TOLERANCE — how exact the color match must be. A value of 15–30 works well for most cases. Higher value = more forgiving (catches similar shades too). Lower value = very strict exact match only.\n• SCAN INTERVAL — how often to check the screen (e.g. every 0.5 seconds)\n• STEP INTERVAL — how long to wait after each click before scanning again\n\nTIP: You can add multiple colors. The detector will click when ANY of them appears on screen — whichever it finds first.": "颜色检测会监视屏幕，并在发现您定义的颜色时立即点击。\n\n• 选择颜色 — 打开取色器以选择精确颜色\n• 从屏幕取色 — 在屏幕任意位置点击以获取该像素的颜色\n• 容差 — 颜色匹配的精确程度（推荐 15–30）\n• 扫描间隔 — 检查屏幕的频率\n• 步骤间隔 — 每次点击后再次扫描前等待的时间\n\n提示：您可以添加多个颜色。检测器在发现其中任何一个颜色时都会点击——以先被找到的为准。",
  "🖼️  Image Detection": "🖼️  图像检测",
  "Image Detection looks for a picture (called a template) on your screen and clicks it as soon as it finds it.\n\n• LOAD IMAGE FILE — pick a .png or .jpg file from your computer\n• FROM CLIPBOARD — if you copied a screenshot, paste it directly here\n• CONFIDENCE — how closely the screen must match your template image. 0.8 (80%) is a good starting point. Lower = more lenient match.\n\nTIP: After each click, the mouse automatically moves to the corner of your screen so it does not block the image on the next scan. This is built-in.\n\nTIP: Use a small, unique part of a button or icon as your template — not the whole screen. Smaller templates match faster and more reliably.": "图像检测会在屏幕上寻找一张图片（模板），找到后立即点击。\n\n• 加载图像文件 — 从电脑选择 .png 或 .jpg 文件\n• 从剪贴板 — 粘贴截图\n• 置信度 — 屏幕需与模板匹配的程度（建议0.8）\n\n提示：每次点击后，鼠标会自动移到屏幕角落，以免遮挡下次扫描。\n\n提示：使用按钮微小且独特的部分作为模板——而不是整个屏幕。",
  "🔀  IF COLOR / IF IMAGE — Conditional Steps": "🔀  如果颜色 / 如果图像 — 条件步骤",
  "IF steps are like a decision point in your automation — imagine a fork in the road where the computer looks at the screen and chooses which path to take.\n\nHow it works:\n1. The computer looks at the screen for a specific color or image\n2. IF it FINDS it → it does the THEN action\n3. IF it does NOT find it → it does the ELSE action\n\nExample — IF COLOR:\n• You are playing a game and you want the bot to click a green button when it appears, but skip and wait when it's not there yet.\n• IF COLOR = green → THEN = click it → ELSE = do nothing\n\nExample — IF IMAGE:\n• You want to check if a 'Loading...' spinner is visible.\n• IF IMAGE = spinner.png → THEN = wait 2 seconds → ELSE = continue clicking\n\nAvailable actions for THEN and ELSE:\n• CLICK FOUND — click exactly where the color/image was found\n• CLICK (fixed position) — click a specific coordinate\n• PRESS KEY — press a keyboard key\n• DELAY — wait a number of seconds\n• STOP — stop the automation completely\n• DO NOTHING — skip and move to the next step\n\nTIP: IF steps are great for automations that need to react differently depending on what's happening on screen — like a game that changes state, or a website that shows different buttons at different times.\n\nTIP: You can set a TIMEOUT for IF steps. If the color/image is not found within that many seconds, the ELSE branch runs automatically.": "IF（如果）步骤是自动化中的决策点。\n\n工作原理：\n1. 检查屏幕\n2. 如果找到了 → 执行 THEN（那么）动作\n3. 如果没找到 → 执行 ELSE（否则）动作",
  "🔴  Record Actions (Macro)": "🔴  记录操作（宏）",
  "The Macro Recorder watches everything you do on the keyboard and mouse, then converts your actions into steps automatically.\n\n1. Open the Record Actions panel\n2. Click START RECORDING (or press the hotkey)\n3. Do whatever you want to automate — type, click, navigate\n4. Press the hotkey again to stop recording\n5. Osenpa Auto Clicker will add all your actions as steps\n\nTIP: Record once, then run as many times as you like.": "宏记录器会监视您的操作并转换为自动步骤。\n1. 打开“记录操作”面板\n2. 点击“开始记录”\n3. 执行日常操作\n4. 按热键停止\n5. 操作将自动添加为步骤。",
  "▶  Running Steps": "▶  运行步骤",
  "Once you have steps in your list, click RUN STEPS at the bottom (or press F7) to start.\n\n• LOOP — run the steps more than once\n• INFINITE — keep repeating until you press STOP\n• STEP INTERVAL — add extra wait time between each step\n• RUN FROM HERE — use the button to start from a specific step instead of from the beginning\n\nTIP: Press F7 to start and stop at any time, even when the app is minimized in the taskbar.": "创建步骤后，点击“运行步骤”（或F7）开始。\n\n• 循环 — 多次执行\n• 无限 — 重复直到按停止\n• 步骤间隔 — 步骤之间的额外等待时长\n• 从此处运行 — 从某一步开始",
  "💾  Profiles": "💾  配置文件",
  "Profiles let you save your panel settings and reload them any time.\n\n• Enter a name and click SAVE CURRENT to save your current settings\n• Select a profile from the list and click LOAD PROFILE to restore it\n• You can save settings from all panels, or just one specific panel\n\nTIP: Create different profiles for different tasks — one for gaming, one for work, one for web automation.": "配置文件可为您保存设置。",
  "⚙  Settings": "⚙  设置",
  "The Settings panel lets you customize the app:\n\n• SHOW ACTIVE TASK INDICATOR — a small overlay in the bottom-right corner shows what is running while automation is active\n• SHOW SCAN AREA BORDER — highlights the region being scanned for color or image detection\n• HOTKEYS — see all current keyboard shortcuts at a glance\n• AUTO-CLOSE TIMER — set the app to close itself after a chosen amount of time (great for setting a session limit)\n• RESET ALL — clear everything and start fresh (your saved profiles are always kept)": "设置面板支持自定义行为。",
  "💡  Tips & Tricks": "💡  技巧与窍门",
  "• Use Ctrl+Z to undo the last change to your step list. Ctrl+Y to redo.\n\n• Add a DELAY step between fast actions to give the computer time to respond. 0.5–1 second is often enough.\n\n• For web automation, use Image Detection to find buttons — it works even when button positions shift around.\n\n• For game automation, Color Detection is faster and more reliable than image matching when targeting a single colored pixel or area.\n\n• Use the PICK AREA button in Color/Image panels to limit scanning to a small part of the screen — this makes detection much faster.\n\n• Export your steps to a JSON file to share them or back them up.\n\n• Press F7 any time to stop an automation — even in the middle of a step.": "• 使用Ctrl+Z撤销，使用Ctrl+Y重做。",
  "❓  Frequently Asked Questions": "❓  常见问题解答",
  "Q: Why doesn't Color Detection find my color?\nA: Try raising the Tolerance value (15–30 is recommended). Lighting, screen scaling, and image compression can all shift colors slightly.\n\nQ: Why doesn't Image Detection find my image?\nA: Make sure the template looks exactly like what's on screen. Try lowering Confidence to 0.7. Use a tight crop of the unique element — avoid templates with lots of background or changing content.\n\nQ: Can I run steps while the app is minimized?\nA: Yes. Once started, automation continues in the background. Use the F7 hotkey to stop it at any time.\n\nQ: Steps are running too fast or too slow — what do I do?\nA: Adjust the INTERVAL on each individual step, or use the STEP INTERVAL in the footer to add a global delay between all steps.\n\nQ: I accidentally deleted my steps. Can I undo?\nA: Yes! Press Ctrl+Z to undo. Osenpa Auto Clicker keeps full undo history.\n\nQ: What is IF COLOR / IF IMAGE used for?\nA: They let your automation make decisions. For example: if a green button appears on screen, click it; otherwise wait. See the IF COLOR / IF IMAGE section above for full details.": "问：为什么找不到颜色？\n答：请提高容差值。",
